---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { Reveal } from '../../components/Reveal';

const title = "Transformative Breathwork — With Miro Kloosterman";
const description = "Transformative breathwork — conscious connected breathing combined with bodywork and sound. In-person or online.";
---

<Layout title={title} description={description}>
  <!-- Section 1 — Hero -->
  <section class="relative h-screen flex items-center px-section-x pt-24 overflow-hidden grain bg-deep-forest">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
      <img 
        src="https://picsum.photos/seed/miro-breathwork/1920/1080" 
        alt="Breathwork Session" 
        class="object-cover w-full h-full opacity-40"
        referrerpolicy="no-referrer"
      />
    </div>
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto w-full z-10">
      <Reveal client:load>
        <div class="max-w-3xl">
          <span class="label !text-gold">Session Modality</span>
          <h1 class="text-white mb-8">Transformative Breathwork.</h1>
          <p class="font-body text-xl md:text-2xl font-light text-sand/80 mb-8 tracking-wide">
            Conscious connected breathing combined with bodywork, movement, and sound. Access and release what the mind can't reach on its own.
          </p>
          <a href="https://tidycal.com/miro-kloosterman/15-minute-meeting" class="btn-primary">Book a Discovery Call</a>
        </div>
      </Reveal>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 2 — The Work -->
  <section class="bg-sand py-section-y px-section-x">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-24">
        <div class="lg:col-span-4">
          <Reveal client:load>
            <h2 class="sticky top-32">What makes it different.</h2>
          </Reveal>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:col-span-8 space-y-12">
          <Reveal client:load delay={0.1}>
            <div class="space-y-8 text-lg font-light text-charcoal/80 leading-relaxed">
              <p>In-person, I bring bodywork and every modality I've trained in into the same session. Breath and touch and sound, all at once. This is what clients tend to mean when they say they've done breathwork elsewhere and never felt anything like this.</p>
              <p>Online, I work with breath alongside specialised hypnotherapy. The depth is different but the work is still real, and for many clients being at home in their own space lets them go somewhere they wouldn't in a studio.</p>
            </div>
          </Reveal>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 3 — Formats -->
  <section class="bg-cream py-section-y px-section-x">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-24">
        <div class="lg:col-span-4">
          <Reveal client:load>
            <h2 class="sticky top-32">Formats.</h2>
          </Reveal>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:col-span-8">
          <Reveal client:load delay={0.1}>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
              {[
                "Group sessions in-person (3 hours)",
                "Private sessions in-person (3-4 hours)",
                "Water breathwork (advanced)",
                "Online sessions (with hypnotherapy)",
                "Ten-session cards (for full arc)"
              ].map(item => (
                <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
                  <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-gold rotate-45 flex-shrink-0"></div>
                  <span class="font-body text-sm font-light text-charcoal">{item}</span>
                </div>
              ))}
            </div>
          </Reveal>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 4 — Who it's for -->
  <section class="bg-sand py-section-y px-section-x">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-24">
        <div class="lg:col-span-4">
          <Reveal client:load>
            <h2 class="sticky top-32">Who this is for.</h2>
          </Reveal>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:col-span-8">
          <Reveal client:load delay={0.1}>
            <p class="text-lg font-light text-charcoal/80 leading-relaxed mb-12">
              Anxiety, depression, panic, shyness, low self-esteem, identity confusion, stuck grief, stored trauma, relationship patterns that keep repeating, chronic pain, asthma, skin conditions, burnout, and the feeling that they're not living anywhere near their full potential.
            </p>
            <div class="bg-deep-forest p-12 grain">
              <h3 class="text-white mb-6">Important: who this isn't for</h3>
              <p class="text-sand/60 font-light text-sm leading-relaxed">
                Breathwork is powerful and there are some conditions where it isn't safe. Please don't book this work if you have cardiovascular problems, high blood pressure, a history of aneurysms, epilepsy, are on heavy medication, have active severe psychiatric symptoms, bipolar depression in an active phase, osteoporosis, recent surgery, glaucoma, are pregnant, are in active addiction, or are in a mental or spiritual emergency. Minimum age is eighteen.
              </p>
            </div>
          </Reveal>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 5 — Testimonial -->
  <section class="bg-cream py-section-y px-section-x">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      <Reveal client:load>
        <blockquote class="pull-quote">
          "What I experienced with Miro was beyond any description. Like I'm leaving my body and then coming back again but as a different person. It really feels like a rebirth."
        </blockquote>
        <p class="font-serif italic text-2xl text-deep-forest mt-8">— Christopher</p>
      </Reveal>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 6 — Closing CTA -->
  <section class="bg-deep-forest pt-section-y pb-16 px-section-x grain relative">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
      <Reveal client:load>
        <h2 class="text-white mb-8">Ready to breathe?</h2>
        <p class="text-sand/60 text-xl font-light mb-16 leading-relaxed">The work starts with a thirty-minute discovery call. No pitch, no script, no pressure.</p>
        <a href="https://tidycal.com/miro-kloosterman/15-minute-meeting" class="btn-primary">Book a Discovery Call</a>
      </Reveal>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
